refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
final public MongoDB\BSON\BinaryMongoDB\Driver\ClientEncryption::createDataKey stringkmsProvider arrayoptions
Creates a new key document and inserts it into the key vault collection.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns the identifier of the new key as a
 MongoDB\BSON\Binary object with subtype 4 (UUID).

&reftitle.errors;

 &mongodb.throws.argumentparsing;
 Throws MongoDB\Driver\Exception\EncryptionException if an error occurs while creating the data key
